text: Discover the charm of this well-kept 4-bedroom home on a corner lot in the desirable Park at Homestead community. Step onto the inviting covered front porch, ideal for unwinding after a long day. Inside, the spacious open-concept living area features a cozy fireplace in the living room, a dining area, and a bright kitchen with a convenient island eating space. Host gatherings on the patio just off the dining area, perfect for BBQs. Large primary suite with a 3/4 ensuite bath plus three additional bedrooms and a full bath upstairs. Enjoy new flooring, A/C, and the convenience of a two-car garage with driveway parking. Plus, a play area in front of the home adds to the appeal. This home is a must see! 1 Year Home Warranty Included!

Immaculate cared for this 2nd owner home in a great neighborhood & adjacent to an 8 acre city owned park. This home is move in ready with recent updates to flooring and baths. 4 could be 5 bedrooms, 3 baths, 2 large living areas, lower level could be another suite with few changes. Large kitchen with lots of cabinets and spacious center island. Spacious rooms throughout, lots of storage plus oversized garage with shop area, newer furnace and AC unit. Presidential roof completed in 2022, trex decking on upper decks, outside kitchen, waterfall, natural gas fire pit and hot tub. The outside entertainment areas are sure to please the fussiest. The house is close to the walking trail and shopping, it is a perfect Lynden location.

Looking for single level living? Check out this 1-story custom home built by Rosendahl-Hancoop on .91 acre parcel w/ 3 bedrooms, 2 full baths and bath. Large primary with on-suite includes separate shower, soaking tub and walk-in closet and private entry off the back deck. Huge picture windows throughout the home brings in abundant natural light. The kitchen offers breakfast bar and eating nook. Spacious living room and dining area or combine the two rooms to create a great room! The 840sq/ft detached shop offers 2-bays w/ nat'l gas heat, 220 power and setup for generator. Expansive covered back deck with a hot tub ready pad plumbed w/ 220 pwr. Convert the shop into an ADU or keep it and build an ADU or two. Buyer to verify with COB.
nearby_schools: Bellingham Public Schools, Northwest Educational Service District 189

text: Picture yourself coming home to a space thats been thoughtfully updated, where new carpet and lighting create a warm, inviting atmosphere. After a day of classes at Western or a productive day at work, youll park in your dedicated, covered spot, knowing your bike is stored securely in the covered racks nearby. Catch up with friends in the open and bright living space, this condo is all about making life simple and comfortable. Everything you need is within easy reachgrab a workout at the on-site gym, or relax in the green spaces around the complex. With easy access to downtown Bellingham, Fairhaven, and trails for those weekend adventures, this home offers both convenience and a sense of calm. Start building your future!

Welcome to 1318 E McLeod Road in the sought-after Northern Heights neighborhood. This charming tri-level home offers 4 bedrooms, 2.5 baths, and 1, 864 sqft of comfortable living space on a generous lot. The main level features a practical layout with two bedrooms, a welcoming living area, kitchen, and dining space that opens to the deckideal for outdoor gatherings. Downstairs, youll find two additional bedrooms, a bonus space perfect for a rec room or office, and access to the outdoor area. The spacious backyard provides ample room for your hobbies and outdoor activities. Centrally located, this well-loved home is ready for its next chapter. Make it yours today!

Rare opportunity in the sought after Samish neighborhood...literally steps from Lake Padden Park! Nestled on 1.77 acres, you'll discover this delightful 4 bedroom 3, 000+ sq ft home plus detached shop! Radiating PNW charm, the vibe here is part mid century modern & part Craftsman, resulting in a warm & inviting home with generously sized rooms. The private primary suite encompasses the entire upper floor & features a fireplace, sitting area, multiple walk in closets (with a second washer & dryer) and luxurious ensuite bathroom. This is an oasis in the city...walk or bike to Galbraith, the park & lake within minutes or relax & entertain on the spacious deck. Detached shop is loaded with potential with bathroom plumbing already in place.

Fabulous opportunity. This custom built home sits on over 1/2 acre with over 100 feet of waterfront in the prestigious Boundary Ridge neighborhood in Semiahmoo. Views from the San Juan Islands to Point Roberts, Tsawwassen and more. Access the beach from the adjacent beach path. Enjoy all the amenities that Semiahmoo offers from the award winning golf course, marina and Resort Semiahmoo.The home is in need of some TLC and repair. It is reflected in the price. The opportunity is tremendous! the spacious layout is fantastic for entertaining and quiet living. The main floor features the primary bed, living room, kitchen and dining with access to enormous deck overlooking the bay and beyond.

Opportunity awaits in this rare corner lot Duplex located in a quiet community near Fairhaven. The highly desirable 3 bedroom and 1.5 bath floorplan in each unit makes it perfect for multi generational living, an investor looking to maximize rental income, or a savvy buyer looking to subsidize their mortgage payment. Property has been updated with a new roof, all brand new windows, new carpeting, and fresh exterior/interior paint. Comes with driveway space for 4 vehicles (2 for each unit) and is fully stocked with all appliances, including a washer/dryer in each unit. Both units were rented this year for $1, 800/month (below market average due to long term tenants), but both units are vacant and ready for you!

Stunning Beach Access Home in Blaine, WA!Discover coastal living at its finest with this spacious 3-bedroom, 2-bath home, ideally located in the serene and scenic city of Blaine, WA. Just steps away from the beach, this property offers the perfect blend of comfort and lifestyle.Boasting a large family room for cozy gatherings and a recreation room for endless entertainment, this home is designed for both relaxation and fun. Enjoy the coastal breeze, stunning views, and easy beach access, perfect for morning walks or sunset strolls.Experience the best of Pacific Northwest living in this prime locationyour dream home awaits!

Escape the ordinary and step into this one-of-a-kind octagonal home, where breathtaking ocean and mountain views meet modern design. Drenched in natural light from high ceilings and abundant skylights, this unique property offers indoor and outdoor living experience unlike any other. This home features 2 beds + den/office & 2 baths, modern kitchen with stainless appliances, wrap around deck, metal roof, full basement/garage and a private backyard. Dont let this architectural delight pass you by!

Welcome to this beautifully updated 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom home, perfectly situated on a spacious, flat lot surrounded by serene woods. With fresh interior and exterior paint, new flooring and trim, and brand-new appliances, this home is move-in ready! You'll love the ample covered parking, providing plenty of space for your vehicles and recreational toys. Ideal as a starter home or for those looking to downsize, this gem offers the perfect balance of comfort and outdoor space. Located in a highly desirable area of the County, you'll enjoy easy access to Blaine, Lynden, and Ferndale, while still maintaining a peaceful, private setting. Don't miss out on this fantastic opportunity. This home is a must see!

Travel back in time to the era where homes have front porches for sitting, and fun, manicured spaces that encourage interaction. This home in Lynden's Homestead is your ticket to community. You are going to love this well-maintained and updated 3BR 2.5 BA home. Great kitchen w stainless and a big island, dining and family room w a slider to your private patio and yard. Light and bright Primary has an ensuite bathroom and walk-in closet. Convenient second floor laundry with washer and dryer included. Large 2 car garage w alley access. You are going to love Lynden, come and see.

Beautiful new construction quality built by Pacific Edge Builders custom home on quiet dead end street. Desirable Whispering Meadows neighborhood is Nooksack's newest development surrounded by protected open space and waterways. This one level 3 bed, 2 bath home features open concept living space which truly feels large. Primary bedroom with walk in closet, tiled flooring and backsplash w/ quartz countertops. Kitchen with stainless appliances, quarts countertops, full height backsplash tile & custom cabinets and large pantry. Large covered patio abutting open space and mature trees provide a private backyard great for entertaining year round. Located close to schools, parks, restaurants, & the Canadian border. Vacant & move in ready!

This Lynden School District gem is a standout property on 4.7 fenced acres. Updated w/a fresh exterior look, including 7-new windows, brand-new roof, & new paint for both the house & the shop. The home features a spacious, open floor plan w/a cozy fireplace & real hardwood floors, in main entry, living room, & kitchen. Enjoy 3-beds+ versatile den/office could serve as 4th bed. w/ space for 5th bed. There are 2.5 bathrooms, & large bonus room above attached two-car garage provides additional living space. Primary bed. conveniently located on main floor. 24x36 shop is a notable feature, equipped w/a 1-bed., 3/4 bath apt. & approx. 700 sq. ft. of space. Shop also includes dbl. overhead doors, wired for generator (gen. remains), & RV parking.

Welcome home to this stunning property in Nooksack! Step inside & get ready to be amazed. The living room features stained shelves & beams with black brackets, adding a modern & stylish touch. The fireplace features marble/stone, douglas fir beams, a TV bracket & stand. The kitchen has soft-close dove-tail cabinets, black quartzite sink, quartz countertops, & a black matte appliance package with slide-in oven. Ginormous 12x25 covered porch in the back is perfect for entertaining. The landscaping is a beautiful & low-maintenance. Upgraded front door & garage door adds a touch of elegance to the home. The exposed concrete in the driveway & porches adds durability & style. Come experience the beauty & craftsmanship firsthand.

Imagine coming home after a refreshing morning run or paddle at Lake Padden just steps from your front door, or a short ride to Galbraiths world-class mountain biking trails! This inviting 3 bedroom, 2.25 bath home is your gateway to an active lifestyle. Fresh updates like a new roof, interior paint, stylish fixtures and remodeled guest bathrooms offer comfortable PNW living. The expansive .33-acre lot features mature landscaping and gardening space in a newly fenced backyard, perfect for relaxation or hosting gatherings. With Whole Foods, REI and other amenities minutes away, everything you need is within reach. Embrace a life where nature meets convenience and community in this sought-after neighborhoodhomes here don't come up often!

Beautiful new construction quality built by Pacific Edge Builders custom home on quiet dead end street. Desirable Whispering Meadows neighborhood is Nooksack's newest development surrounded by protected open space and waterways. This one level 3 bed, 2 bath home features open concept living space which truly feels large. Primary bedroom with walk in closet, tiled flooring and backsplash w/ quartz countertops. Kitchen with stainless appliances, quarts countertops, full height backsplash tile & custom cabinets and large pantry. Large covered patio abutting open space and mature trees provide a private backyard great for entertaining year round. Located close to schools, parks, restaurants, & the Canadian border. Vacant & move in ready!

Heres your chance to own a builders custom home on a large corner lot in one of the most coveted neighborhoods in Lynden. Main-level living including a spacious primary suite connected to a private courtyard with a covered porch. Upstairs youll find 3 bedrooms, a home office, and a large bonus room with surround sound. Youll love the custom details including open-beam ceilings, Juliet balcony, built-ins, stonework, and hand-scraped hardwood floors. Other amenities include a large 2-car garage and central A/C. This home seamlessly blends craftsmanship and modern comfort. Don't miss out!

This Coronado plan emphasizes style, comfort and convenience. With voluminous 9 ft ceilings, the main level includes an open dining room, an impressive great room with gas fireplace, a high-end gourmet kitchen featuring a double oven, gas range and massive center island for you and yours to gather around, as well as a main floor bedroom with an adjacent bathroom. Upstairs reveals a spacious loft, two generous bedrooms with a shared bath plus an elegant owners suite boasting an expansive walk-in closet and deluxe bathroom. CENTRAL HEATING/COOLING INCLUDED! If you are working with a licensed broker please register your broker on your first visit to the community per our site registration policy. ASK ABOUT SPECIAL FINANCING.

Cozy studio condo situated just steps from WWU, South Hill & Fairhaven. Why rent when you can buy? With just one owner it has been well-kept. Interior has fresh paint & cleaned carpets. It is move-in ready or priced to update then move-in. With no rental cap, it works great for a rental. Convenient parking is available and also central to bus lines. Spacious storage closet in unit for tools, gear, or more. Hard to find a home at this price in Bellingham! Upcoming assessment of approximately $40, 000 for new siding & windows will be paid for by seller!

Welcome to the Robin Lane Community, where this well-maintained, move-in ready home awaits! Bathed in natural light, the open layout flows seamlessly, creating a warm and welcoming atmosphere. The spacious primary bedroom features a luxurious en suite bathroom, while the large laundry room and ample storage throughout the home add to its functional charm. Step out to the covered patio, perfect for relaxing or entertaining, with plenty of space for gardening, plus a shed for your tools and extra storage. The carport and ample parking are added bonuses. With easy access to parks, trails, the bus line, and the vibrant Fairhaven shops and businesses, this home is a perfect blend of comfort and convenience!

Discover easy living in this Gleneagle Villa townhome, nestled within the highly desirable Semiahmoo Community. Offering the convenience of main floor living, this home has a comfortable yet elegant floor plan, enhanced by vaulted ceilings & new flooring throughout. Open layout connects the living and dining areas, while maintaining distinct spaces perfect for entertaining or quiet relaxation. This well-maintained property, managed by a responsible HOA, is perfect for downsizers looking for the convenience of lock and leave living without the worry of exterior upkeep or landscaping. So many amenities just around the corner - golf, marina, spa & health club, and more! There's truly no better place to call home than Semiahmoo.

Discover your dream home on the 9th Fairway of Homestead's renowned golf course! This charming single-level residence features vaulted ceilings, a gas stove, a wall of windows + a bright skylight creating a warm & inviting atmosphere. The spacious primary suite boasts a large walk-in closet & a luxurious en-suite with a double sink vanity & jetted tub. Loaded with storage throughout! Enjoy peace of mind with a new furnace (2021) & hot water tank (2023), + a recently updated roof. Set on a sprawling 16, 988 sq ft lot, youre just a short walk from restaurants, fitness club, Bender Fields, & scenic trails. With stunning northern views & lovely sunsets, this is the ideal blend of comfort & lifestyle! Dont miss out on this golf course gem!

You will never find anything like this in Lynden. Imagine being steps from Fairway Center, yet often visited by resident deer & spawning salmon. Parklike & sprawling 1/2ac creekside lot. Separately available is an 11, 000sqft adjoining lot. Custom 4/5 bd, 3.5 ba home perched high above Fishtrap Creek & packed w/desirable features. Oversized bedrooms, endless storage, rec rm, bonus rm, wrap around deck, new furnace, central vac, intercom, A/C, & an oversized 720sqft garage. Complete custom rebuild in 2007. Spacious main floor owners suite w/covered deck & walk-in closet. Stunning kitchen, huge island, double oven, exposed beams, counters & cabinets galore & views to creek. Backyard flows into Dickinson Park w/8 ac of mostly forested parkland!

Potential awaits for this 1920's charmer! This promising 2 bed, 2 bath fixer resides on 2.5 acres with 40x48 heated & insulated 220 power shop with 14 foot door, large fenced yard, fruit trees, open kitchen w/eating bar & dining space, SS appliances, wood floors & unfinished basement. Primary bedroom leads out to the backyard & patio, offering ample space for enjoying your surroundings. Don't miss out on this chance to invest in your vision with a touch of TLC. Only 15 minutes to Bellingham! SOLD AS IS!

Welcome to 884 Hemlock Court, in the 55+ community of Pepin Creek. This charming single level 3-bedroom, 2-bath home offers an open floor plan with Italian porcelain tile flooring throughout the main living areas, gas fireplace with custom built-ins, sunny breakfast nook, & upgrades throughout. The primary suite features a sitting area, along with a spacious en-suite bathroom & walk-in closet. Two additional bedrooms provide versatility for guests or an office. Enjoy the beautiful English-style garden & patio; fully fenced with garden shed. A perfect spot for relaxing or entertaining. Located in a beautiful community with included lawncare, easy access to shopping, dining, & outdoor activities, this home offers both comfort & convenience.

Dreaming of stunning lake views without breaking the bank? This charming PNW gem delivers just that, offering peekaboo water views from nearly every room and potential rental income. Step outside onto the spacious deck, perfect for soaking up the sun and equipped with a propane hookup for your BBQ's, plus a slider from the primary bedroom that lets you greet the tranquil lake each morning. Inside, you'll find Brazilian cherrywood floors and cabinetry, along with a recently updated primary bathroom. The downstairs has a separate entrance and kitchen, which adds to the home's versatility, which has been operating as a short term rental. All the furniture is also for sale. Roof was replaced in 2021. It doesn't get much more turn key than this.

Discover your dream home in beautiful Sudden Valley! This meticulously maintained home, located in Gate 2, has new interior & exterior paint, new carpet, & is situated on a quiet, dead-end street that gets loads of sunshine! Features vaulted ceilings, gas fireplace, French doors, covered back deck & primary room w/large walk-in closet & ensuite! With 4 bedrooms (3 up, 1 down) & 3 bathrooms, this property offers ample space for comfortable living. Kick back and relax on the private patio & enjoy the mature landscaping. An extra large garage can be easily used as a workshop space. Easy walk to the AM/PM beaches, community centers & pools!

Discover this exceptional property in Ferndale, boasting an unobstructed view of Mt. Baker. The estate features two residences and an RV site equipped with 50-amp electric service, sewage dump, and water. Initially sold as a 2-bedroom, 2-bath home with 1245 square feet, the property now includes a new manufactured home added in 2023, offering 3 bedrooms, 2 baths, and 1280 square feet of living space. With a 3-bedroom septic system installed, the property is marketed as a 1-bedroom in the front house and a 2-bedroom in the rear. The front house's rent is $2300, while rear house was rented for $2500. Front home features 3 fireplaces, 2 balconies, cherry cabinets, quartz counter tops & tile floors. Perfect for investment or multi-fam living!

Remodeled and move in ready! This home features the perfect blend of comfort and affordability, offering an open-concept kitchen & living area, complete with stainless steel appliances. Unwind on your choice of two decks, ideal for enjoying your morning coffee. With new windows, siding, and insulation, this low-maintenance home is energy-efficient and designed for year-round comfort. The home also features a convenient storage shed that doubles as a utility room. Priced under $100, 000 with low space rent, this property offers exceptional value for quality living. Motivated Seller dont miss out on this opportunity! Owner financing available.

South Side Top Floor Condo is move-in ready & priced to sell! Brand new carpet & a fresh coat of interior paint greet you while they brighten & freshen the space. This corner unit brings in light from south & west-facing windows & features a south-facing balcony with a partial view of Chuckanut Mountain. The kitchen includes stainless appliances + the in-unit washer & dryer come with it as well. The open Studio sleeping space is divided by an optional (non-bearing) partition wall, creating a closable bedroom & separate office or large dressing room. Plenty of closet space + the unit comes with a storage space large enough for a bike or ? in the common hall. Light, localized wear on the Formica or vinyl factor into the attractive price.

Want a little relief from the grind? Oriental Ave may be the place for you. Desirable neighborhood of 1/2 acre lots, majestic mature trees and mid century homes that combine to create a secure feeling of peace and contentment. This 1954 beauty is ready to be reinvigorated if so desired but may be perfect for you as is. Exposed beams highlight the 1493 sf, 3 bed interior. Easy horseshoe driveway, nice private side-yard area and a platform deck w/firepit in the back highlight the grounds and make it easy to enjoy this whole setup. The 3.5 acre wooded county park that abuts the rear property line only adds to the equation. Upside and potential are obvious.

Welcome to Birch Bay! This fixer-upper is a great opportunity to create your dream home just a short walk from the beach. Nestled on a greenbelt lot, the spacious yard has potential for landscaping improvements and revitalizing the existing pond and flower gardens. Inside, the 4-bedroom layout boasts vaulted ceilings but needs some updates to reach its full potential. The large master suite features a jetted tub, perfect for a remodel. With new flooring and painted white trim already in place, you can easily add your personal touch. This property is a blank canvas waiting for your vision. Dont miss this chance to invest in a home in a beautiful location and make it uniquely yours!

Desirable rambler in the Barkley neighborhood! Featuring 3 bedrooms, 1.75 baths & nestled in a sought-after community, offering both comfort and convenience & located on a quiet non-thru Residential Street. Featuring a spacious open floor plan w/vaulted ceilings, new carpet, gas fireplace, & new exterior paint. Close by to great shopping & restaurants, with Barkley Village, Sunset Square & IMAX Theater only a few blocks away! With a private backyard ideal for outdoor gatherings, this property is not just a houseit's a place to create lasting memories. Located near excellent schools, parks & local amenities this home truly has it all. Dont miss your chance to make it yours!

The Ivy by MainVue Homes at Horizon is a stunning design you do not want to miss. Upon entry find a soaring Two-Story Foyer a corner set a Home Office. Deeper into the home, the Two-Story Great Room is paired perfectly with a dining room and mutually connected Gourmet Kitchen flush with 3cm Quartz counters, Stainless Steel Appliances, and a Grand Butlers Pantry. For even more space, a main floor Multi-Purpose Room is tucked just off the kitchen. Upstairs, look out onto the Great Room from the front-facing Leisure room that leads to three secondary bedrooms and the luxurious Grand Suite. Customer registration policy: Buyers Broker to visit or be registered on Buyers 1st visit for full Commission is reduced.

Don't miss this spacious 2, 558 sq ft home! The main-level primary bedroom features an en suite bath with double sinks and a large walk-in closet. The expansive kitchen offers granite countertops, bar seating, and a walk-in pantry. With 3 full baths, each bedroom enjoys its own. Downstairs, you'll find a large office/den and an enormous, versatile family room for games, crafts, or play. Enjoy the outdoors on two huge decks, (one on each level) with serene woods behind and Beaver Ridge Park with trails in front. Plus, a heat pump provides A/C for those warm summer days! Come enjoy the beauty of Sudden Valley and enjoy the many beaches, parks, marina, and huge off leash dog park right on Lake Whatcom.

Solid 2 bd 1 bth home and detached 2 car heated garage/shop on a sweet little 2.8 acres. This property has huge potential to be so much more, and it's awesome just the way it is. This is a well-crafted home w recent upgrades that include energy efficient heat/AC mini split system in home and garage. The acreage is level and would be easy to make it your own happy place. Whether you clear a few trees to enhance the view, look into adding your new dream home and shop somewhere on the parcel or leave it exactly as is, this is a good value! This home may feel nice and private but you're only 1.3 miles from I-5 and the waterfront hamlet of Blaine w all its recent upgrades along w award winning golf and restaurants. Would be a great rental too.
